    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mineral Defense</strong> 是一款独特的塔防与Roguelite玩法结合的游戏，战略选择无穷无尽！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过解锁地块和设计完美路径来塑造战场。规划交叉路口和瓶颈，最有效地引导敌人前进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与独特的敌人战斗！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用塔和技能的组合击败敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以使用多种攻击和支援塔。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >减缓敌人，降低他们的抗性，用酸液融化他们，然后用导弹将他们炸飞！这只是制定高效生存策略的众多方式之一。选择权在你手中！ <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125890/extras/8e036b974f5b720742eb2fc75ce89ab4.poster.avif?t=1743397558\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125890/extras/8e036b974f5b720742eb2fc75ce89ab4.webm?t=1743397558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125890/extras/8e036b974f5b720742eb2fc75ce89ab4.mp4?t=1743397558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>解锁强大的升级！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每轮结束后抽取卡牌以解锁强大的升级，激活新结构，并提高你的胜利几率。<br> <br><strong>超过100</strong>种游戏内奖励，并且还在不断增加！ <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125890/extras/1f88367fa979ec4a563c8181f143694e.poster.avif?t=1743397558\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125890/extras/1f88367fa979ec4a563c8181f143694e.webm?t=1743397558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125890/extras/1f88367fa979ec4a563c8181f143694e.mp4?t=1743397558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>研究新技术！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用收集到的研究点解锁新技术。探索强大建筑的潜力，释放毁灭性的技能，投资高风险催化剂，并通过升级强化你的武器库。<br> <br><strong>184</strong>种独特的研究条目，每周都会新增内容！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125890/extras/1d931cd673cbd382962f325e7f5cf01a.poster.avif?t=1743397558\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125890/extras/1d931cd673cbd382962f325e7f5cf01a.webm?t=1743397558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125890/extras/1d931cd673cbd382962f325e7f5cf01a.mp4?t=1743397558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>随时保存！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mineral Defense</strong> 提供保存功能，让你可以轻松从上次进度继续游戏。游戏将在每波结束时自动保存你的进度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可调节的游戏速度！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们知道不是每个人每天都有足够的时间来玩游戏。<strong>Mineral Defense</strong> 提供4种可调节的游戏速度，让你以最适合自己的节奏进行游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入社区！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mineral Defense</strong> 的Discord服务器是一个活跃的社区，在这里你可以分享你的想法、提出建议、报告漏洞，或者只是放松聊天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过信息标签中的链接加入我们吧！</p>",
